*Morate* da se potrudite da biste dobili dobre rezultate. (You must make an effort to get good results.)
*Morala* bi da se obratite nekom stručnjaku. (You should have consulted a professional.)
*Moramo* da poštujemo zakone. (We must respect the laws.)
*Morali* smo da se suzdržimo od komentara. (We had to refrain from comments.)
*Morate* li da se obratite lekaru? (Do you have to see a doctor?)